RDT Trading System Database Migrations
======================================

This directory contains Alembic database migrations for the RDT Trading System.

Directory Structure
-------------------
- env.py          : Alembic environment configuration
- script.py.mako  : Template for generating migration scripts
- versions/       : Directory containing migration scripts

Usage
-----
Use the db_migrate.py CLI tool in the scripts/ directory:

    # Initialize/upgrade to latest
    python scripts/db_migrate.py upgrade

    # Create a new migration
    python scripts/db_migrate.py migrate -m "Add new column"

    # Downgrade one revision
    python scripts/db_migrate.py downgrade

    # Show migration history
    python scripts/db_migrate.py history

Or use Alembic directly:

    # Upgrade to latest
    alembic upgrade head

    # Generate migration from model changes
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

    # Downgrade
    alembic downgrade -1

Environment Variables
---------------------
- DATABASE_URL or RDT_DATABASE_URL: Override the database connection URL
- Default: sqlite:///data/rdt_trading.db
